OL,3,COn board the flying hospitals taking
OL,4,Cseriously injured Palestinians to
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FITV News Global Security Editor Rohit
OL,8,FKachroo was allowed onto one of the
OL,9,Fevacuation flights, from just inside
OL,10,FEgypt's border with Gaza to Qatar,
OL,11,Fwhere they will receive treatment.
OL,13,FThe sun was setting over the El Arish
OL,14,Fairfield, less than 30 miles from the
OL,15,FRafah border crossing, but it felt
OL,16,Fmore like a new dawn than dusk.
