OL,3,COn board the flying hospitals taking
OL,4,Cseriously injured Palestinians to
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FAs Palestinian patients were pushed in
OL,8,Ftheir wheelchairs, or carried on
OL,9,Fstretchers up the steps towards the C-
OL,10,F17 transporter, they were in every
OL,11,Fsense on an upward path.
OL,13,FFor the 29 evacuees and their families
OL,14,Fboarding a Qatari Air Force plane to
OL,15,FDoha this journey offered a fresh
OL,16,Fchance.
OL,18,FA chance to receive the medical help
OL,19,Fthey simply could not get in Gaza and
OL,20,Fwith it, the chance for survival.
