OL,3,COn board the flying hospitals taking
OL,4,Cseriously injured Palestinians to
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FSince the Emir of Qatar announced
OL,8,Fplans to treat 1,500 injured people
OL,9,Ffrom Gaza, there have been 18 flights
OL,10,Ffilled with patients.
OL,12,FThey are picked up, then flown the
OL,13,Fthree hour flight from Sinai to Doha.
OL,15,FOn board, doctors carry out medical
OL,16,Fprocedures and counsellors hold
OL,17,Fsessions with children.
OL,19,FSo far around 450 are receiving
OL,20,Ftreatment in Doha, with some of their
OL,21,Ffamily members housed nearby.
