OL,7,F"When I see... 30 patients, around 30
OL,8,Fpatients - I (have to) control myself
OL,9,Fto continue my work," says Hashem
OL,10,FNaeem Darwish of Qatari Islamic
OL,11,FRelief, and one of the organisers of
OL,12,Fthe evacuation mission.
OL,14,FHe fights back tears as he introduces
OL,15,FITV News to the patients who fill the
OL,16,F20 beds set up for the sickest
OL,17,Fpatients.
