OL,4,Cseriously injured Palestinians to
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FOne of them is Israa, who is wearing a
OL,8,Fsurgical mask to conceal her eyes. "I
OL,9,Fwas going to visit my sister, when the
OL,10,Fwindow blew up in my face," she
OL,11,Fexplains. "Lots of pieces of glass hit
OL,12,Fmy eyes. I hope that God and the
OL,13,Fdoctors can make me see again."
OL,15,FShe has lost the sight in one eye but
OL,16,Fis hoping that doctors in Doha will be
OL,17,Fable to save the other.
OL,19,F"Going to Qatar means I will go back
OL,20,Fto life. I feel isolated from life at
OL,21,Fthe moment," she said.
