OL,7,F"I will continue to study. I was
OL,8,Flearning to be architect, I have one
OL,9,Fyear left to graduate and I was the
OL,10,Ftop of my year with distinction."
OL,12,FAfter touchdown there is one decision
OL,13,Fleft for the doctors to take. Who
OL,14,Fshould be allowed off the flight
OL,15,Ffirst, to receive hospital treatment?
OL,17,FThey select 13-year-old Abdullah - a
OL,18,Fboy with a bandaged head with severe
OL,19,Ffacial burns and fractured arms who
OL,20,Fhas, at points, been screaming during
OL,21,Fthe fight to Qatar.
